{"tid":496722,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同一球場一周兩宗 男子足球場內猝死","createTime":"2017-12-12T03:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T12:27:31.000Z","uid":60281,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b003d783b07e273262002912d82b10d1ad888487","tid":496722,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港仔黃竹坑遊樂場，早上7時許，保安巡經公園一個足球時，發現一名身穿球衣的男子倒卧觀眾席旁地上，昏迷不醒，於是報警，救護員到場，證實男子已告死亡，警方封鎖現場，調查男子死亡原因。現場發現死者少量個人物品及兩對波鞋。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者年約40歲，被發現時已死去七至八個小時，估計他與友人昨晚踢波後，友人先行離開，事主獨自一人在場邊休息時不適暈倒，失救而死。<br />\n<br />\n上周二凌晨4時半，一名59歲姓袁的士司機，偕數名行家在香港仔黃竹坑遊樂場球場踢足球，其間事主突然不適，繼而暈倒地上，昏迷不醒，行家見狀立刻召救護車，將他送院，惜搶救無效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171212/57570250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57570250&d=Yt7A02elDoz4Cy37BAznh4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4495f3dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57570250&h=e428d210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171212/57570250</a>"},{"pid":"4c7d3a00041b4305e8201891c04329842f2d47f4","tid":496722,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP"},{"pid":"31740c316c876f656a2c20d3b6e55637fc1ff4ff","tid":496722,"uid":34490,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"踢過幾次呢個場"},{"pid":"4e49c76d065afe579da22f26e5d7c86e318ec69b","tid":496722,"uid":1255,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:47:27.000Z"